<placeName cert="high" full="yes">Oxyrhynchus</placeName></head><div type="edition" lang="grc" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><div type="textpart" n="r" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="1"/>Ἀκύλας Σαραπίωνι 

    <lb n="2"/>χαίρειν. 

    <lb n="3"/>κομισάμενός σου τὰ γράμ-

    <lb n="4"/>ματα πάνυ ἥσθην. ᾗ μάλιστα 

    <lb n="5"/>ὁ ἡμέτερος Καλλίνεικος ἐμαρ-

    <lb n="6"/>τύρει περὶ τῆς διαίτης σου ἧς 

    <lb n="7"/>ποιῇ καὶ ἐν τοιούτοις ὢν 

    <lb n="8"/>πράγμασι<del rend="erasure" status="unremarkable">ν</del>, μάλιστα μὴ 

    <lb n="9"/>ἀφιστάμενος τῆς ἀσκήσεως. 

    <lb n="10"/>ἄξιον οὖν ἐστιν ἐπαινεῖν ἑ-

    <lb n="11"/>αυτούς, οὐχ ὅτι ποιοῦμεν ταῦ-

    <lb n="12"/>τα ἀλλὰ ὅτι μὴ ἐξαγόμεθα 

    <lb n="13"/>ὑφ᾽ ἑαυτ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ῶν</supplied>· ἀνδραγάθ<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ε</unclear><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ι</supplied> οὖν 

    <lb n="14"/>καὶ τὰ λοιπὰ ἐπιτέλεσον 

    <lb n="15"/>ὡς ἀνὴ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ρ ἀ</supplied><unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">γα</unclear>θός, καὶ μ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ή σ</supplied><unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ε</unclear> 

    <lb n="16"/>ταρασσέ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">τ</supplied><unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ω</unclear> ἢ πλοῦτος ἢ ὥρα 

    <lb n="17"/>ἢ ἄλλο τ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ι τ</supplied>ῶν <choice><corr>τοιούτων</corr><sic>τοιου<del rend="erasure" status="unremarkable">ν</del>των</sic></choice>, ὡς 

    <lb n="18"/>οὐδὲν <unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ὄφ</unclear><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ελ</supplied>ός ἐστιν ἀρετῆς 

    <lb n="19"/>μὴ παρούσης, ἀλλὰ φροῦδα καὶ οὐ-

    <lb n="20"/>δενὸς ἄξια. θεῶν σωζόντων 

    <lb n="21"/>προσδέχομαί σε ἐν τῇ Ἀντινόου. 

    <lb n="22"/>τὸ σκυλάκιον πέμψον Σωτη-

    <lb n="23"/>ρίδι, ἐπεὶ αὐτὴ νῦν ἐν ἀγρῷ <choice><corr>δια-

    <lb n="24"/>τριβει</corr><sic>διατρειβει</sic></choice>. <choice><corr>ἔρρωσο</corr><sic>ερρωσσο</sic></choice> σὺν τοῖς σοῖς. 

    <lb n="25"/><choice><corr>ἔρρωσο</corr><sic>ερρωσσο</sic></choice>. 
</ab></div><div type="textpart" n="v" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="26"/>Σαραπίωνι   φιλοσόφωι 

    <lb n="27"/>παρὰ Ἀκύ<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">λου</unclear> 

    <lb n="28"/>φίλου. </ab></div></div><div n="meta.30336" type="description" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><rs type="material" cert="high">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.30336" type="commentary" subtype="textDate" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p><date type="textDate" notBefore="201" notAfter="400">III - IV</date></p></div><div n="meta.30336" type="commentary" subtype="general" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p>Zum Ort vgl. Z. 21.</p></div><div n="meta.30336" type="bibliography" subtype="principalEdition" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><listBibl default="NO"><bibl type="publication" subtype="principal" default="NO"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">P.Oxy.</title><biblScope type="volume">42</biblScope><biblScope type="numbers">3069</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="Trismegistos" default="NO"><biblScope type="numbers">30336</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="DDbDP" default="NO"><series>0181</series>; <biblScope type="volume">42</biblScope>; <biblScope type="numbers">3069</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref type="Perseus" href="0181;42;3069" evaluate="all" from="ROOT" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.30336" type="bibliography" subtype="illustrations" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><p>keine</p></div><div n="meta.30336" type="bibliography" subtype="otherPublications" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><head>Andere Publikation</head><bibl type="publication" subtype="other" default="NO">Tibiletti, Lettere private 20</bibl></div><div n="meta.30336" type="bibliography" subtype="translations" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><head>Übersetzungen</head><listBibl lang="en" default="NO"><head lang="de">Englisch:</head><bibl type="translations" default="NO">Trapp, Letters (2003), Nr. 35 (mit Text).</bibl></listBibl><listBibl lang="fr" default="NO"><head lang="de">Französisch:</head><bibl type="translations" default="NO">Burnet, L'Égypte ancienne (2003), Nr. 214